Anywayssssss, there has been many ups and downs in this piscine, many hurdles, obstacles and forgotten semicolons but it has made me a stronger and better person, if it wasnt for everyone ive met, all the people whove ive talked to, id have never made it this far. Thank you to everyone who was by my side, no matter if you're smart, hardworking, generous, friendly, polite, gullible (cough cough) or just funny. Youve all pushed me day by day without you guys i would have been lost. You've all made my month all the way down to the seconds, tho i may have shed a few too many tears i am grateful for everything and everyone ive done and met, i have no regrets and i hope yall have none to. No matter where life takes you and me, I'm sure we can overcome it. Cadet or no cadet, lets face life head on, together.
